        "subject": "LU-1187 osd: refine object exists check in OSD/MDD",
        "message": "LU-1187 osd: refine object exists check in OSD/MDD\n\ndt_object_exists should always > 0 inside OSD, in case\nsome remote object access OSD accidently.\n\nIn MDD/MDT/LOD layer, there might be remote objects as\nwell, so object_exists might either > 0 or < 0.\n\nChange-Id: Ie0bfb17b457f1bf66f1200982c7dfb03359daeaa\nSigned-off-by: Wang Di <di.wang@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
